1077
01:31:11,760 --> 01:31:15,116
Rocky. What brings you here tonight?

1078
01:31:16,320 --> 01:31:18,880
Mr Jergens, the poster's wrong.

1079
01:31:19,000 --> 01:31:23,755
- What do you mean?
- I'm wearin' white pants with a red stripe.

1080
01:31:27,120 --> 01:31:32,319
It doesn't really matter, does it? I'm sure
you're gonna give us a great show.

1081
01:31:33,200 --> 01:31:36,476
Try to get some rest, kid. Good night.

1082
01:33:05,240 --> 01:33:07,310
I can't do it.

1083
01:33:09,600 --> 01:33:11,636
What?

1084
01:33:11,760 --> 01:33:13,716
I can't beat him.

1085
